ğŸ® Overview
Find the Blockchain is a fun, daily mini-game built with React and Vite! Each day, a "winning" blockchain is randomly selected from a curated list of popular ones (like Ethereum, Solana, Bitcoin, and more). Your challenge? Guess which one it is in as few attempts as possible.

Daily Reset: A new winner every 24 hours â€“ perfect for a quick daily check-in.
Simple Mechanics: Input your guess, get feedback (e.g., "Too early/late in the alphabet" or direct hints), and reveal the answer at the end.
Educational Twist: Learn about different blockchains while playing!

This project started as a basic React + Vite template and has been enhanced with game logic, UI polish, persistence (via localStorage), and mobile responsiveness. Whether you're a crypto newbie or a blockchain pro, it's a lighthearted way to engage with the ecosystem.
Why this game? In a world of complex DeFi and NFTs, sometimes you just need a silly guess-the-word-style game... but with chains!
ğŸš€ Features

Daily Challenge: One puzzle per day, seeded by date for consistency across devices.
Guess Feedback: Color-coded hints (green for correct, yellow for close, gray for way off) inspired by Wordle.
Score Tracking: Track your streaks and best guesses locally.
Blockchain List: Pre-loaded with 20+ real blockchains (e.g., Ethereum, Polkadot, Avalanche).
Responsive Design: Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile.
Dark/Light Mode: Auto-detects your system theme.
Shareable Results: Copy a spoiler-free emoji summary to share your score.

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

Frontend: React 18.x with hooks for state management.
Build Tool: Vite 5.x for lightning-fast development and builds.
Styling: Tailwind CSS for rapid, utility-first design (added for better UX).
State Management: Zustand for lightweight global state (guesses, scores).
Persistence: localStorage for daily progress.
Linting & Formatting: ESLint + Prettier for clean code.
Testing: Vitest + React Testing Library (basic setup included).
Deployment: Ready for Vercel/Netlify (see Deployment section).

No backend required â€“ everything runs client-side!
ğŸ“¦ Installation

Clone the Repository:Bashgit clone https://github.com/ManiacXHG/Find-the-blockchain.git
cd Find-the-blockchain
Install Dependencies:Bashnpm installThis sets up React, Vite, Tailwind, Zustand, and all dev tools.
Run the Development Server:Bashnpm run devOpen http://localhost:5173 in your browser. Hot Module Replacement (HMR) will auto-reload on changes!

ğŸ¯ Usage

Start Playing:
Load the app â€“ today's puzzle awaits!
Type a blockchain name (e.g., "Ethereum") in the input field.
Hit Enter or click "Guess" to submit.

Hints & Rules:
6 Guesses Max: Like Wordle, but shorter for quick plays.
Feedback:
ğŸŸ© Green: Correct position.
ğŸŸ¨ Yellow: In the name, wrong spot.
â¬œ Gray: Not in the name.

Win Condition: Guess correctly within 6 tries.
End of Day: Reveals the answer and resets tomorrow.

